sellerCard.description: I've built over 500 websites on different platforms, ensuring they look great, work smoothly, and adapt to different devices. I always tailor my work to meet the client's needs, but most importantly, I build websites that convert clients and drive sales. I use Webflow, Squarespace, Shopify, and WordPress. If you'd like to see examples of my work or discuss your project, please don't hesitate to ask!

description.content:
Your Vision, My Skills and Experience


If you're searching for a professional Squarespace web designer with extensive experience who can create a website that makes you proud, you're in the right place.


As a certified Squarespace Expert and Squarespace Circle Member, I prioritize user-friendly designs, mobile responsiveness, and SEO optimization. Most importantly, I focus on crafting solutions that work. This approach ensures that my work stands out from the rest. Having designed over 500 projects, I'd be happy to share examples. Feel free to contact me today!


I also work with Webflow, WordPress, and Shopify. If you're interested, feel free to text me!


Features:


  • Non-templated custom design based on your vision, needs, and goals
  • Making changes until you are completely satisfied
  • Basic SEO optimization
  • Custom coding for additional features
  • Mobile responsive design
  • 20% subscription discount for the first-year website plans (annual subscriptions only)
  • Design from scratch / Redesign / Revamp
  • Providing premium stock Images/videos
  • Lifetime Q&A and bug support
  • (Bonus) Personalized video-guide, to help you manage the website on your own


Let's discuss your project today!

Kirill.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What clients do you work with?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I carefully review each project before accepting it. I know what value I can bring, therefore I am very meticulous with whom I work with. My main niches are: health & wellness, home services and interior design, e-commerce brands, and real estate niches (agents, developers, architects, agencies).

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I book you any time?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Due to the constant workload, I usually need to plan the order at least a few days in advance. Please contact me and I'll confirm my current availability.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you create the content (text and images) as well?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If the client doesn't have any content, I can provide professional stock images, videos, and iconography. I am not able to provide professional texts or graphic design (logos, custom illustrations or graphics, etc.)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you the owner of the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: First I create the website (If the client does not have it already). Then, after we finish, I transfer the ownership to my client. It means the client gets all the possible rights and is able to remove me from the site as well if desired.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you help me to choose the color scheme, fonts and a template?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. As a professional in website development and UX/UI design, I provide my clients with the best ideas for their businesses. So if you don't know which way to go, be assured I am able to help you out.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What makes you different?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I am genuinely interested in helping my clients grow, instead of just building a nice design. So far, I have designed and developed hundreds of websites focused on growth and scaling, establishing a strong online presence for every client I work with.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you help me after we finish?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I provide lifetime support for every client. However, I don't create new pages or make any sufficient changes to the website for free. But I am always open to help if there are any questions or issues concerning the website created.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you work in different timezones?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sure! There is no problem for me to work in any time zone.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is there anything I should know about Squarespace before starting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please get acknowledged with Squarespace subscription and domain costs. There is no need to know more than that to have a live website. All the hard work is on me, and for all further questions, I am there to help as well.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have a question and I don't see an answer here. What should I do?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please contact me and I'll try to help :)

His creativity, talent, and vision exceeded my expectations by a mile. If you're looking for someone to bring your website to life with expert craftsmanship and innovation, I highly recommend working with him!

Kirill is awesome -- this was an exceptional experience.  Kirill's gorgeous work speaks for itself, but what you can only know from working with him is how he really gets what the client is looking for and is able to turn your ideas and vision into a reality.  We love our website and have received non stop compliments.  You should definitely hire him -- he's a bargain for the quality of work you get.  Excellent communication, expectation setting, and helpfulness too!

seller_response.comment: Thank you so much! It means a lot 🙏🏼

reviews.comment: Kirill was great to work with. I had an idea of what I wanted but Kirill made it come to life. My team was slow to get Kirill what he needed but he was patient and was able to help us on our own pace. I would definitely work with him again in the future. Very professional and I'm very happy with the finished site.
Second time hiring for website overhaul and couldn't be happier! Every few years we need a refresh and will look forward to hiring again in the near future!

Kirill Illenkov has truly outdone himself with ANOTHER incredible website redesign! His work is impeccable—professional, well-documented, and completely bug-free. Plus, his politeness and proactive communication make working with him a breeze 👍. I highly recommend Kirill for any web development needs!

reviews_snippet.comment: I've been managing my company for 18 years now and I've worked with several hundred contractors over the years. I can honestly say that it does not get any better than Kirill. He has a very well established process for working with people, he thinks of everything ahead of time, the quality of his work is exceptional, and he is extremely responsive throughout the whole process. Kirill is simply the best person to work with if you need to have a website made.
I can’t say enough great words about Kirill! The experience from begging to end was flawless and the work was top notch. I can see why he is a very high rated pro.

AMAZING EXPERIENCE & RESULTS!!! Kirill is an incredible human being to work with!! Professional, Patient, Polite, Great lateral thinker & fantastic at his job! His attention to detail is exceptional & he went above & beyond what I expected.

I’ve built a few websites before with other developers & this is the first website I have been 100% truly happy with.

I can’t say enough positive things about Kirill & his work. If you’re as pedantic as me & have high standards then definitely work with Kirill. I look forward to working with him on future projects!
Second time hiring for website overhaul and couldn't be happier! Every few years we need a refresh and will look forward to hiring again in the near future!

Kirill is ABSOLUTELY amazing! His attention to detail and professionalism resulted in an aesthetic and functional website that exceeded all expectations. Polite, cooperative, and timely—working with him was seamless, and I can't wait for future projects! 👌
